These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, iced-tea, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, gardening, filmmaking, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, classical, country, techno
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan techno##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the fan classical##6
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking iced-tea or the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan country, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan folk have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan country##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the fan techno##5
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person drinking 7up and the fan folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | cola      | 7up    |
| Hobby         | reading     | filmmaking | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | country       | folk | techno         | classical     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapes, blueberry, grapefruit
There are 4 different nationalities: german, pakistani, turkish, thai
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, chinchilla, cat
 1. the german is the person eating grapefruit or the owner of the cat is the german, but not both##10
 2. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 3. the german is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
 4. the owner of the chinchilla and the german have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 8. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
11. the thai is in an even position##4
12. the german is the person eating cauliflower or the german is the owner of the cat, but not both##10
13. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | grapefruit | grapes    | cauliflower | blueberry    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | german | pakistani  | thai |
| Pet           | chinchilla     | cat    | goldfish    | dog    |

