.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, water, fanta
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lemon, cabbage, cucumber
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, colombian, australian, polish
1. the person eating cucumber is the indian##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
3. the person eating cucumber is the polish or the person eating cucumber is the person drinking cola, but not both##10
4. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
5. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the colombian is between the person eating eggplant and the indian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | fanta         | water     | cola | 7up |
| Food          | eggplant | lemon | cucumber         | cabbage   |
| Nationality   | australian     | colombian   | indian       | polish   |

