.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, papaya, plum, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, puzzles, chess, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, american, indian
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the japanese##1
 2. the brazilian is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the brazilian##6
 6. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the american or the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating papaya, but not both##10
 8. the american is the person eating plum or the american is the person who's hobby is puzzles, but not both##10
 9. the indian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating plum##7
10. the indian is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | peach  | strawberry   | papaya | plum  |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | chess  | puzzles | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | brazilian | japanese | indian  | american |

