.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, superhero, epic, drama
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, rat, dog
 1. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the ferret is not the person watching superhero movies##6
 3. the owner of the goat is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
 4. the person drinking mirinda is not the person watching drama movies##6
 5. the owner of the dog and the person watching thriller movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person watching thriller movies or the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the ferret, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
11. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking water##7
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | water | mirinda | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | superhero    | thriller   | drama |
| Pet           | ferret    | goat | rat    | dog  |

