There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, canadian, thai, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, car, helicopter
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 2. the malaysian is the person who's hobby is video-games or the malaysian is the person driving the helicopter, but not both##10
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
 4. the person driving the bus and the japanese have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 6. the japanese is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 7. the canadian is on the far right##1
 8. the thai is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the malaysian##7
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the japanese is between the person driving the car and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games   | rock-climbing | gardening  | photography |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | thai      | japanese | canadian |
| Transport     | bike | bus       | helicopter    | car   |

