.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, cherry, pear, peas
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, pilot, police-officer, photographer
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, goat, horse
 1. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
 2. the nurse is between the owner of the turtle and the person eating peas##2
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the photographer##3
 4. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the owner of the hamster##7
 5. the owner of the hamster and the person eating cucumber have the same parity positions##9
 6. the pilot is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the police-officer is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 8. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is the nurse or the owner of the turtle is the person eating pear, but not both##10
10. the owner of the turtle and the pilot have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | pear    | cucumber     | peas         | cherry |
| Job    | pilot | nurse    | police-officer | photographer    |
| Pet    | turtle      | hamster | goat            | horse   |

