The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, reading, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, action, family, zombie
 1. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
 6. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
 9. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
10. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is reading or the person who's hobby is reading is the person eating watermelon, but not both##10
11. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
