 4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person driving the trike is not the engineer##6
 6. the photographer is between the accountant and the engineer##2
 7. the person driving the snowmobile and the journalist have different parity positions##9
 8. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the snowmobile or the person watching martial-arts movies is the photographer, but not both##10
10. the person driving the trike and the person watching martial-arts movies have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |       4       |
