.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, raspberry, lettuce, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, zombie, action
4 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, snake, goat
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching zombie movies or the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating lemon, but not both##10
 3. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 4. the person eating lettuce is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 5. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
 6. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 8. the person eating raspberry is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
10. the owner of the rat is not the person watching action movies##6
11. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
12. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
14. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | raspberry   | lemon | mango  | lettuce        |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | action      | zombie    | musical |
| Pet           | snake   | goat    | guinea-pig | rat      |

 